title: Early Lab Test Shows Omicron Weakening Vaccine Effectiveness
content:
1. Early Lab Test Shows Omicron Weakening Vaccine Effectiveness  The Wall Street Journal
  2. Pfizer shot offers partial protection against Omicron variant, study finds  CBS Evening News
  3. Omicron significantly reduces Covid antibody protection in small study of Pfizer vaccine recipients  CNBC
  4. Live Updates: Pfizer Vaccine Gives Some Protection Against Omicron, Early Study Shows  The New York Times
  5. First lab results show omicron has 'much more extensive escape' from antibodies than previous variants  The Washington Post
